msgid "Speed Instinct"
msgstr "迅捷本能"

msgid "Only while this mutation is selected, weapon attack speed increases with active Boss Cells: 0 cells +0%, 1 cell +20%, 2 cells +30%, 3-4 cells +40%, 5 cells +50%."
msgstr "只有选择这项变异时，武器攻击速度才会随已激活 Boss 细胞提高：0 细胞 +0%，1 细胞 +20%，2 细胞 +30%，3-4 细胞 +40%，5 细胞 +50%。"

msgid "The harsher the island becomes, the faster your hands remember how to survive."
msgstr "岛屿越险恶，你的双手就越快想起该如何活下去。"

msgid "Cell Vitality"
msgstr "细胞活力"

msgid "Only while this mutation is selected, each enemy killed increases maximum health by active Boss Cells x 100. At 0 cells, it grants no bonus."
msgstr "只有选择这项变异时，每击杀一个敌人都会使最大生命值增加已激活 Boss 细胞数 x 100。0 细胞时没有加成。"

msgid "Reforge to random Legendary quality"
msgstr "重铸为随机金色品质"

msgid "Alchemic Forge"
msgstr "炼金铸造"

msgid "Unlocks the \"Reforge to random Legendary quality\" option at the underground forge, where you can spend gold to reforge an item into a random Legendary."
msgstr "在小铸造所解锁「重铸为随机金色品质」选项，可花费金币把一件装备重铸为随机的传奇（金色）品质。"
